GET	/api/storymaps/{storyMapId}	获取指定校园故事地图的详细信息:
需要返回的格式：
{
  "storyMapId": "uuid-string",
  "title": "Old Library's History",
  "description": "A journey through time...",
  "authorId": "uuid-string",
  "createdAt": "timestamp",
  "coverImageUrl": "http://...",
  "location": {
    "locationId": "uuid-string",
    "lat": ...,
    "lng": ...,
  },
}